<app-segmented-toggle
    legend="Show performance using data from"
    [(ngModel)]="matchType"
    (ngModelChange)="emitChange()"
  >
    <app-segmented-toggle-item
      name="match-type"
      identifier="estimated"
      value="estimated"
      label="Estimated"
    />
    <app-segmented-toggle-item
      name="match-type"
      identifier="evidenced"
      value="evidenced"
      label="Evidenced"
    />
  </app-segmented-toggle>
